comment: Rivers (LAC) makes marginal contact with Hayward (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Correctly called 24 second violation.
Jordan (LAC) and Hill (UTA) make incidental contact with one another during the loose ball.

Paul (LAC) maintains legal guarding position on Hill's (UTA) drive toward the basket.
Jordan (LAC) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.

Paul (LAC) makes body to body contact with Hill (UTA) that affects his SQBR.
Paul (LAC) pushes Gobert (UTA) and the contact affects his FOM off ball.
Paul (LAC) pushes Gobert (UTA) while the ball is in flight.
All technical fouls are reviewed after each game by League Operations.

Paul (LAC) commits a take foul on Hayward (UTA).
Payton (ORL) makes incidental contact with Collison (SAC) that does not affect his SQBR.
